# Sign Out Button: Red Highlighted Everywhere

## Rule

**All Sign Out buttons across the platform must use the shared `SignOutButton` component** with consistent red styling (text-destructive, bg-destructive/10, hover:bg-destructive/15).

## Component

- **Path:** `components/sign-out-button.tsx`
- **Variants:** `sidebar` (full button with label) | `icon` (icon-only for headers)

## Usage

```tsx
import { SignOutButton } from '@/components/sign-out-button'

// Sidebar footer (patient, pro, nurse, etc.)
<SignOutButton onClick={handleSignOut} label="Sign Out" className="flex-1" />

// Header icon button
<SignOutButton variant="icon" onClick={onSignOut} label="Sign Out" />
```

## Where It Applies

- Patient dashboard sidebar
- Professional dashboard sidebar (doctor, nurse, pharmacy, clinic, laboratory, ambulance)
- Super-admin sidebar
- Header dropdown and mobile menu (use `text-destructive bg-destructive/10` for consistency)
- Any new dashboard or layout added in the future

## Do Not

- Use raw `Button` with `LogOut` icon for Sign Out
- Use `text-muted-foreground hover:text-destructive` for Sign Out
